- Demonstrated experience developing rich applications with HTML5/CSS/JavaScript;
- Highly skilled in React/Typescript and proficient in using functional components with hooks;
- Experience implementing and developing in ReactJS (preferred) or other SPA frameworks;
- Experience working with OAuth2/ODIC authentication in front-end applications;
- Ability to write high-performance, reusable UI code and appropriate unit testing;
- Experience with cross-browser/device development;
- Extensive knowledge of software design patterns and best practices;
- Experience with frontend applications that are compliant with WCAG 2.1 AA standards;
- Experience with debugging and resolving performance issues.
- Ability to work collaboratively in an Agile team;
- Familiarity with Frontend build tools, CI/CD pipelines, test automation (Jest/Cypress), common AWS technologies, Jira, Confluence, and Git;
